The paper focuses on spatial query processing and optimization in a distributed setup, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of spatial indexing techniques and query optimization also aligns with topics in data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the use of bitmap filters is a technique commonly used in network infrastructure (cs.NI).
